हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: In a ruthless corporate jungle, a gifted woman hides her deepest scars while chasing impossible dreams. Love, rivalry, and betrayal twist her path, making every step feel like walking on fragile glass. Will her courage carry her to triumph—or shatter everything she’s built?
